snippet.title: Hardhat Willy (protoype) for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Game description:

You are Willy and you have to kill parts of a centipede, steal a hard hat from a bird and destroy eggs with it, repair broken walls and watch out for Pac-Man...uhm, I mean "Waka Waka".

While the parts of the centipede do not hurt you, they can steal whatever hard hat you wear. Waka Waka and red walls can kill you, however.


What I think:

Quite fun game. Shame that it was never released...

As I don't rate prototypes, no matter how good or bad they are (or how far\close they are of being finished), I didn't rate Hardhat Willy either...would be unfair to the other prototype videos I have. ;)
